<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></title>
    <link rel="SHORTCUT ICON" href="./favicon.ico">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/vnd.microsoft.icon" href="favicon.ico">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alegreya:wght@400;700&family=Overlock&family=PT+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="whatis">
      <a href="#">What is Webathena?</a>
    </div>
    <div id="info">
      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <img src="<%= require('./images/about1.png') %>" alt="The Kerberos three-headed dog">
          </td>
          <td>
            <img src="<%= require('./images/about2.png') %>" alt="A user running 'zwrite clyde' and another user claiming to be clyde">
          </td>
          <td>
            <img src="<%= require('./images/about3.png') %>" alt="Diagram of a user communicating with a service and the KDC">
          </td>
          <td>
            <img src="<%= require('./images/about4.png') %>" alt="MIT SIPB grumpy fuzzball">
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <b>Webathena</b> is a browser-centric implementation of the <b><a href="http://web.mit.edu/kerberos/">Kerberos</a></b> network authentication protocol.
          </td>
          <td>
            Kerberos provides a secure means for <b>users</b> and <b>services</b> to prove their identities to each other, even over insecure networks.
          </td>
          <td>
            It ensures that your password <b>never leaves this page</b> in any form, and services <b>never have more permissions</b> than they need.
          </td>
          <td>
            Webathena is a project of MIT <b><a href="http://sipb.mit.edu/">SIPB</a></b>. &copy;2013 davidben and cesium, &copy;2021 asedeno, released under the <b>MIT license</b>.
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
    <header>
      <div id="logo">
        <img src="<%= require('./images/eye-small.png') %>" style="left: 78px; top: 12px">
        <img src="<%= require('./images/eye-large.png') %>" style="left: 87px; top: 16px">
        <img src="<%= require('./images/eye-large.png') %>" style="left: 105px; top: 16px">
        <img src="<%= require('./images/eye-small.png') %>" style="left: 121px; top: 12px">
      </div>
      <h1>Webathena</h1>
    </header>
    <webathena-alert></webathena-alert>
    <webathena-ui></webathena-ui>
  </body>
</html>
